<% if @user %>
You requested a password reset for the CoughDrop login, "<%= @user.display_user_name %>".

To finish resetting your password you'll need to open this link in your web 
browser and enter a new password:

<%= JsonApi::Json.current_host %>/<%= @user.user_name %>/password_reset/<%= @user.password_reset_code %>

If this message was sent in error please disregard it and your password will not be changed.

Thanks!
- The CoughDrop Team
<% else %>
You requested a password reset for one of the CoughDrop logins tied to this email address.

To finish resetting your password you'll need to click the link for the correct login below.

<% @users.each do |user| %>
"<%= user.display_user_name %>" - change the password for this login:
<%= JsonApi::Json.current_host %>/<%= @user.user_name %>/password_reset/<%= @user.password_reset_code %>

<% end %>
Thanks!<br/>
- The CoughDrop Team
<% end %>